nodes.text: The second season of the animated Star Wars: The Clone Wars television series, marketed under the name Rise of the Bounty Hunters, began airing on October 2, 2009 on Cartoon Network, starting with the episodes "Holocron Heist" and "Cargo of Doom" and ending with the final two parts of the "Boba Fett Trilogy" on April 30 2010. It began airing in the UK on October 24 on Sky Movies, and in Spain on November 20 on Antena.Neox. On April 4, Cartoon Network began the airing of the series to all Latin America. It began airing on Cartoon Network in the UK on April 19, and in Italy on April 16.
